screens, $3,458 per screen, $15.7 million, eight weeks.
   7. ``Lethal Weapon 2,'' Warner Bros., $1.6 million, 1,356
screens, $1,185 per screen, $140.1 million, 12 weeks.
   8. ``The Abyss,'' 20th Century Fox, $1.5 million, 1,176 screens,
$1,286 per screen, $49.7 million, seven weeks.
   9. ``Kickboxer,'' Cannon, $1.432 million, 963 screens, $1,486
per screen, $10 million, three weeks.
   10. ``Turner &amp; Hooch,'' Disney, $1.426 million, 1,208 screens,
$1,180 per screen, $63.8 million, nine weeks.
